{"tid":904878,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「80後」鄉委書記個人照滿頭灰白掀熱議 當局稱「條件很艱苦」","createTime":"2018-11-16T16:52:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-16T19:27:47.000Z","uid":28765,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a49e6d38d76d279e19379c69ff003aeadfd0117c","tid":904878,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T16:52:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181116/s00004/17bafba3aebae6aa85f525f009788a7d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181116%2Fs00004%2F17bafba3aebae6aa85f525f009788a7d.jpg&h=8291eb97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181116/s00004/17bbde4a902a106502241e9d81a7331d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181116%2Fs00004%2F17bbde4a902a106502241e9d81a7331d.jpg&h=5485fd2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雲南省楚雄州委組織部，昨（15日）發布一批幹部任期的公告，當中一名「80後」擬提名為大姚縣政協副主席的候選人，其個人照掀起內地網民熱烈討論，有人質疑他是否「80後」，笑言：「是把他爹照片不小心放上來了嗎」。但亦有網民反擊，希望大家「嘴下留情」，認為基層幹部的壓力和工作量非常大。<br />\n有關公告指出，這名出生於1980年8月的縣政協副主席候選人，名為李忠凱，有大學學歷，1999年步入職場，現任大姚縣灣碧鄉黨委書記，曾任該縣灣碧鄉人大主席等職；又在本年10月被中共楚雄州委評為「楚雄州擔當作為的優秀基層幹部」，指擬提名李忠凱為大姚縣政協副主席候選人。<br />\n然而，公告配上的照片顯示，李忠凱卻幾乎一頭白髮。有網民留言質疑，他是否確實38歲，開玩笑地指「我們80後太辛苦了」，「把他爹照片不小心放上來了嗎」，「你也不知道他發生了什麽經歷了什麽導致了這樣的健康狀態」。<br />\n另一邊廂，有網民為當事人抱不平，認為基層幹部的壓力和工作量很大，「別嘲諷，真的還是很多為了讓社會更好才考公務員的人」。<br />\n據內地傳媒引述工作人員回應表示，當局可肯定的照片是李忠凱本人，「年齡也對得上」，解釋他早年由村幹部做起，直至鄉鎮幹部等，一直均在基層工作，而現時任職的大姚縣灣碧鄉也是楚雄州最偏遠的鄉鎮之一，條件很艱苦。<br />\n（楚雄彝族自治州人民政府網頁/新京報）<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181116/s00004/1542362735082\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181116%2Fs00004%2F1542362735082&d=w85OPF0jygj%2F2z1%2BvXTwmYsQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=34265390\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181116%2Fs00004%2F1542362735082&h=2a5fa84a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181116/s00004/1542362735082</a>"},{"pid":"0d5232a5771ff48265b8f67b396eb66f83e8dd2b","tid":904878,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T16:53:34.000Z","msg":"1880<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdea0196d99dabb50af9fcb836d4a7fc1df16fc7","tid":904878,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T16:54:55.000Z","msg":"條眼眉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fae3108ebfca8de9f38aed4c4794adfad75bfb2a","tid":904878,"uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T16:55:58.000Z","msg":"80歲後<br />\n<br />\n個look算後生"},{"pid":"1853943f3ebfe4980c5cca3e34fa69b752b02d51","tid":904878,"uid":136773,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T17:08:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rCvFCLC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrCvFCLC.jpg&h=414b4053&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n人又80後 佢又80後"},{"pid":"c781267b7430c92088dc6ee92fcc53ce323a8732","tid":904878,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T19:25:09.000Z","msg":"80歲後呀"},{"pid":"3b553fad1e8a166397717969909551c16d574bb8","tid":904878,"uid":27112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T19:27:47.000Z","msg":"用蝗語講，呢個書記會唔會&rdquo;長得過份著急&rdquo;？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}